Edited [`content/papers/microwaves.md`](/home/dave/Projects/jaynes-archive/content/papers/microwaves.md) with structural QA-only changes.

### Summary of changes
- Inserted blank-line paragraph boundaries around display equations/prose transitions so Hugo+KaTeX renders cleanly (no prose glued to `$$...$$` blocks).
- Added minimal equation-number tags to early untagged display equations:
  - `\tag{1}` through `\tag{5}` in Chapter I, so in-text references to equations `(4)` and `(5)` are now resolvable.
- Repaired malformed markdown table in “Experimental Confirmation”:
  - fixed header to `| Method | Value of $Q_u$ |`.
- Normalized broken footnote markdown formatting in `[^13]` (removed stray unmatched emphasis markers) without changing meaning.

### Self-check
- Paragraph breaks intended as boundaries are now blank-line separated around affected structural problem areas (especially around equations).
- No unresolved in-text equation references to missing display-equation numbers were found.
